## Summary
This documentation page details the Settings page in Amplitude, covering organizational settings (including plan usage, user management, and Session Replay configuration) and personal settings (profile management, site preferences, notifications, and theme options). It explains how admins can configure organization-wide settings while all users can manage their individual preferences.

